metadata.name: Support
metadata.description:
Support is important for everyone. Words spoken at the right moment can save a person, they can give strength to move on and not give up. Support helps us grow and develop, gives us a sense of confidence.
That's why it's always so important to me that people are attentive to each other, that they don't pass each other by. After all, even the smallest word of support can change someone's life.
